<h2>Hex Keypad</h2>
<p>
Default 2 hex keypads is configured. The second keypad is configured by selecting checkbox 'VP580 Expansion Keypad' (orange ellipse) or checkbox 'VP590 Colour Board' (yellow ellipse). The only known game using 2 keypads is the Chip-8X game blockout.
</p>
<p>
To change and view the hex keypad to PC key mapping select the 'Key Map' button (green ellipse), see also section <a href="KeyMappingMain.htm">Key Mapping</a>
</p>
<h2>Keyboard</h2>
<p>
To use the VIP with ASCII keyboard support select the keyboard checkbox (blue ellipse). 
</p>
